{
  "stem": "23645.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When the Russians were advancing on the Eastern Front, there was a lot of commotions, and people were beginning to celebrate.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They thought, oh, great, we're going to-- to make it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're going to-- to survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One other incident that comes to mind that I should tell you that happened-- I was friends with one young fellow that was a bit older than me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His name was Schmiel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in the munitions factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One day, these huge belts that drive the-- the machines-- when they wore out, they would be discarded-- thrown in the garbage.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he picked up a piece of that and cut it in-- in pieces so that we could put it in the inside of our shoes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of our shoes were worn down, you know, and when it was cold and wet, this sort of gave a little protection.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would bundle up our feet in-- in paper, as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave me some of those-- a piece-- and I put it in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was spotted, taking that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I thought that one of the SS men noticed both of us having it, but I wasn't noticed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That day, he got picked out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were made to stand in a circle, after work, after we got back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this SS man said, no one steals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wasn't stealing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It-- He picked it up from the garbage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No one steals from the Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And without any ceremony at all, he took out the revolver and shot him, point blank.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was quite close to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, some of the-- his blood spilled on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And here, again-- you know, I'm just telling you about close calls.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
